text: Brittany Anne Trish Byrnes (born 31 July 1987) is an Australian movie and television actress. She has been acting since she was seven. Her known roles are Thea Hawkins in Search for Treasure Island, Hannah Schuller in Escape of the Artful Dodger and Charlotte Watsford in H2O: Just Add Water. ==Other websites== * Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Australian movie actors Category:Australian television actors Category:Australian child actors
